rComments: Worst prof I’ve taken in my 4 years of studying. He is extremely lazy and never answers emails. His lectures are extremely boring.Drop this course if you can I do not recommend this « professor » he shouldn’t be teaching. Plus he removed the option to grade the course because he knows how terrible he is.

Avoid if you have the choice. Very insolent, gives no feedback. Incoherent dans ses formulations. If you ask him to clarify something, he will write you a whole essay telling you why you're asking the question instead of just answering it. Final exam is usually 3h but we had 30m. doesn't care about your success and boring voice. I am warning y'all

I had to give 2 feedbacks cuz I had other things to say. When we had to evaluate our teachers, his survey wasn't there because he knows all things we were going to say. we had to contact the faculty. Acts nice on zoom because they're recorded but as soon as we had questions at the end of the lecture, he would stop recording and put down his mask.

The worst experience I have ever had. The worst teacher known to man. If it is not mandatory DONT TAKE THE CLASS. He is so rude whenever you send emails asking questions, he refuses to share the powerpoints of bright space, he barely gives anytime to complete exams literally 30 mins !!!! When we ask for help he says that were the problem.

This is my first time ever rating a prof. Avoid this man if you can. The way that he phrases things in the test makes no sense and is not compatible with what was learned in class. He does explain properly what he wants from you and is such a tough grader. Also, he gives no feedback for the midterms. I have never done this badly in a class...

Contextual with his explanations, which helps concretize the material in a real-life context. But a terrible people person and not very accommodating with his students. Very difficult to reach as he does not answer any of his e-mails and avoids answering questions during class breaks or office hours.

Terrible teacher, he takes everything personal. Talks to you like youre fresh out the womb, respects you less than a dog and grades your work with his eyes closed. Avoid him at all cost. Even if you have to change you undergrad.
Notes de cours inaccessibles en ligne, environnement d'apprentissage difficile, évaluations vagues et organisation mal effectuée.
Very Good

Il connaît bien ce qu'il enseigne. Il est drôle mais super arrogant et n'accepte pas de critiques. Il peut te mettre dans un état d'embarras si tu dis quelque chose qu'il n'aime pas. Ces cours sont ok, mais beaucoup de matériels. Évitez si vous pouvez.

tu peux avoir une bonne note dans son cours. Mais, se présenter en classe est une perte de temps. On apprend rien en classe! Il vaut mieux faire ses lectures et lire ses notes chez soi. Si vous avez le choix, je vous conseille de prendre un autre professeur.
Funny prof! Definitely knows his stuff and made going to class enjoyable. 100% would take his class again!!

Hes a nice teacher, I had him in another class which students had poblems with his attitude but he somehow changed and I started to like him more! Gives us example of questions for exam but mostly uses them on exam which is helpful due to the ambiguous teaching.  Took 2 classes with him and would still take more!

Je ne recommande pas ce prof. Il est drôle et gentil en tant que personne mais ce n'est pas le meilleur en tant que prof. Ses explications ne sont vraiment pas claires, ses exemples non plus! ses critères sont flous et il corrige de façon assez incohérente. Il a retiré les notes de cours de bbl avant l'exam et il n'est pas d'une grande aide!

Ce prof méprise ces étudiants au plus haut point, il manque de professionnalisme et d'éthique. Comes across as very arrogant, cannot accept constructive criticism only gives out negetive and MEAN feedback.   If you can change prof, DO IT.  Si vous pouvez évitez ce prof, FAITES LE.

Il connait sa matière mais n'explique pas d'avantage pour pouvoir comprendre la leçon sans revoir ces notes et powerpoints. Utilise des exemples qui son utile et explique biens les examens de classe. Si tu es bon en économie et c'est une matière qui t'intéresse, tu aimeras ce prof.
Vraiment un bon prof ! Très drôle mais un peu arrogant! Ses examens comprennent majoritairement des questions à choix multiples vraiment ressemblantes à celles des examens exemples sur C.V
Ce prof MÉPRISE les étudiants. Il s'en fout carrément. Don't take his class, it's horrible.

Excellent professeur!Il sait rendre vivant un savoir qui n'est pas du tout évident.  Est toujours prêt à recevoir et à aider.Donne de très bons conseils.Les exemples sont efficacement unique. L'assistant de très grande utilité.  Merci à vous.Je recommande fortement.
Méprisant à un nouveau niveau. Ses assistants son bêtes et désinteressés. Enseigne la matière de manière très inéfficace. Très monotone. Changez de prof si vous en avez l'opportunité.
Pas organisé, très méprisant envers les étudiants. He's not organized and he doesn't like students. Furthermore, he's really not willing to help, even if you really need it!
Ennuyeux comme c'est pas possible, pas organisé, dit qu'il donnera les notes, oublie de le faire. Est drôle cependant. Si vous pouvez avoir un autre prof, changez!
